  Purpose:     Process the web request.
  Parameters:  <none>
  Notes:       
------------------------------------------------------------------------------*/
  
    {lib/checkloggedin.i}

    
    FIND this-user
        WHERE this-user.LoginID = lc-global-user NO-LOCK NO-ERROR.
    
    ASSIGN
        ll-customer = this-user.UserClass = "CUSTOMER".
        
